quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  32,12,"(Ìwọ ìbá rí èèmọ̀) tí ó bá jẹ́ pé o rí àwọn ẹlẹ́ṣẹ̀ nígbà tí wọ́n bá sorí kọ́ ní ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa wọn, (wọ́n sì máa wí pé): “Olúwa wa, a ti ríran, a sì ti gbọ́ràn (báyìí), nítorí náà, dá wa padà (sí ilé ayé) nítorí kí á lè lọ ṣe iṣẹ́ rere; dájúdájú àwa ni alámọ̀dájú.”",""
  32,13,"Tí ó bá jẹ́ pé A bá fẹ́ ni, dájúdájú A ìbá fún gbogbo ẹ̀mí kọ̀ọ̀kan ní ìmọ̀nà rẹ̀, ṣùgbọ́n ọ̀rọ̀ náà ti ṣẹ láti ọ̀dọ̀ Mi (báyìí pé): “Dájúdájú Mo máa mú nínú àwọn àlùjànnú àti ènìyàn ní àpapọ̀ kún inú iná Jahanamọ.”",""
  32,14,"Nítorí náà, ẹ tọ́ ìyà wò nítorí pé ẹ ti gbàgbé ìpàdé ọjọ́ yín (òní) yìí. Dájúdájú Àwa náà yóò gbàgbé yín (sínú Iná). Ẹ tọ́ ìyà gbére wò nítorí ohun tí ẹ̀ ń ṣe níṣẹ́.<sup>1</sup>","[1] Allāhu kì í ṣe onígbàgbé. Nítorí náà, ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al-Baƙọrah; 2:15."
  32,15,"Àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ nínú àwọn āyah Wa ni àwọn tí ó jẹ́ pé nígbà tí wọ́n bá fi ṣe ìṣítí fún wọn, wọn yóò dojú bolẹ̀ ní olùforíkanlẹ̀, wọn yó sì ṣe àfọ̀mọ́ pẹ̀lú ìdúpẹ́ fún Olúwa wọn. Wọn kò sì níí ṣègbéraga.",""
  32,16,"Wọ́n ń gbé ẹ̀gbẹ́ wọn jìnnà sí ibùsùn. Wọ́n sì ń pe Olúwa wọn ní ti ìpáyà àti ìrètí. Wọ́n sì ń ná nínú ohun tí A pèsè fún wọn.",""
  32,17,"Kò sí ẹ̀mí kan tí ó mọ ohun tí A fi pamọ́ fún wọn nínú àwọn n̄ǹkan ìtutù ojú. (Ó jẹ́) ẹ̀san ohun tí wọ́n ń ṣe níṣẹ́ (rere).",""
  32,18,"Ǹjẹ́ ẹni tó jẹ́ onígbàgbọ́ òdodo dà bí ẹni tó jẹ́ òbìlẹ̀jẹ́ bí? Wọn kò dọ́gba.",""
  32,19,"Ní ti àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, tí wọ́n sì ṣe iṣẹ́ rere, àwọn ibùgbé (nínú) Ọ̀gbà Ìdẹ̀ra ń bẹ fún wọn. (Ó jẹ́) ohun tí A pèsè sílẹ̀ (dè wọ́n) nítorí ohun tí wọ́n ń ṣe níṣẹ́ (rere).",""
  32,20,"Ní ti àwọn tó balẹ̀jẹ́, Iná ni ibùgbé wọn. Ìgbàkígbà tí wọ́n bá fẹ́ jáde kúrò nínú rẹ̀, A ó sì máa dá wọn padà sínú rẹ̀. A sì máa sọ fún wọn pé: “Ẹ tọ́ ìyà Iná tí ẹ̀ ń pè ní irọ́ wò.”<sup>1</sup>","[1] Āyah yìí dúró sórí àwọn kèfèrí àti munāfiki, kì í ṣe mùsùlùmí ẹlẹ́ṣẹ̀ tí ó kọ́kọ́ wọ inú Iná ṣíwájú kí ó tó wọ inú Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra."
